    "en": {
      "title": "Who are those 8 people?; Notification issued by the police",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police have requested the public's help to find 8 people connected with the murder of former Member of Parliament Amarakirthi Athukoral.",
        "It has also been requested to provide information related to 8 persons related to this murder incident to the telephone numbers 011 251 4217 or 071 859 2868.",
        "It is noteworthy that following the violent incidents on May 9th, former Member of Parliament Amarakirthi Athukorala was attacked and killed by thugs at the Negombo junction."
      ],
